{"tid":251271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教琴分享音樂！！","createTime":"2017-05-20T18:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T21:35:30.000Z","uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d158fc07b850f9309735f545d19f68b3e45081","tid":251271,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T18:10:37.000Z","msg":"小弟由中一偶然愛上鋼琴，就不自禁沉迷其中，最終考到ATCL演奏級啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩畢業，想搵下愛鋼琴的巴絲，如果你地未搵到老師，可以俾個機會我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享我所感受到的音樂！！<br />\n<br />\n由於我教琴經濟尚淺，只有數年伴奏經驗，加上志在分享音樂，學費勁低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一條件係你要有琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁你對鋼琴的愛才可以一直延續下去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe1500a09ff6bb06ada428f7339214f0c9497d3","tid":251271,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"有興趣可以加我TG:TonmyFF"},{"pid":"a7bafee2f7c6ceb88bc7d1d4043551387af38d70","tid":251271,"uid":117602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T18:22:37.000Z","msg":"巴打諗住收幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17e5d17cb6c13c024bc5388728c9bf058a08abc","tid":251271,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T19:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打諗住收幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇番你幾級，住邊<br />\n我既價錢出而搵唔到架，無論私人定琴行<br />\n而家想磨下時間同令多d人愛上鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e6dd56314f6e48b64236168350e5af83afd0bc","tid":251271,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T19:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打諗住收幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"